{"tid":2442754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"每天至少打3次才能睡！他崩潰求診竟開口「這要求」醫嚇傻","createTime":"2021-03-11T14:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T17:38:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb4559a39c7815c509e65202dc0a55ec8c45862","tid":2442754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"泌尿科醫師邱鴻傑近日在節目表示，一名年輕氣盛的男大生求診時透露，自己每天至少要「DIY」3至4次才能安心入眠，否則晚上就會焦慮到無法入睡，嚴重影響到生活作息；沒想到對方下一句竟開口指定要「這種藥物」，讓他立刻拒絕勸退，「萬一造成你永久性不舉，你10年後一定會恨我！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2879711-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2879711-PH.jpg&h=de70fa99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲21歲男大生有自慰成癮的困擾，導致生活嚴重受到影響。（圖／翻攝自醫師好辣YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2879712-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2879712-PH.jpg&h=47929c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邱鴻傑在《醫師好辣》表示，該名男大生有「自慰成癮」的困擾，倘若一天沒有達到3至4次，晚上就會焦慮到睡不著，間接造成白天沒精神，「他還滿聰明，上網去搜尋一些資訊，所以一來門診，開宗明義跟我講說，『醫生，我就是性成癮方面的問題，你可不可以開某一類的藥物給我。』」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2879714-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2879714-PH.jpg&h=af2756db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼邱鴻傑表示，男大生一天至少要3-4發，否則晚上就會焦慮到無法入睡。（圖／翻攝自醫師好辣YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/13/2879713-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F13%2F2879713-PH.jpg&h=861c4358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但男大生提出的藥物是用來治療攝護腺肥大、抑制男性賀爾蒙的藥品，甚至還提到了治療攝護腺癌的第二類藥物。邱鴻傑一聽趕緊拒絕，「我不可能開給你」，因為這些藥物恐怕會造成永久性不舉，「你10年後一定會恨我！」<br />\n<br />\n邱鴻傑透露，性愛成癮與自慰成癮概念相同，大多是沉迷高潮的那段過程，如果民眾有輕度性成癮的話，可以培養其他興趣轉移注意力，比如說運動或打電動都可以。他最後透露，男大生之後被轉介給身心科，透過抗焦慮藥物和轉移注意力，情況已經獲得改善。"},{"pid":"f14e1aff516d03348b4d22b2ac2a73c04a665db2","tid":2442754,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"你扯唔起點打三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e9055937d14d84ab17369873462dd6f1bb226a","tid":2442754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14e1aff516d03348b4d22b2ac2a73c04a665db2","tid":2442754,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"你扯唔起點打三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"請大家戒丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9653bec506743cda1004585d5d36b57a5ab32b","tid":2442754,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"我都每日打2次3...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5540253284bf8003088dba962fbcca86ae8e844","tid":2442754,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"牙腸戒咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6315af9a3368d608b25646855acead8cba49c1","tid":2442754,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:36:35.000Z","msg":"搵女伴解決即可，每日服用三劑<br />\n藥到病除"},{"pid":"8641364be26ffda7bc2711df73b1bb37e00d65de","tid":2442754,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5540253284bf8003088dba962fbcca86ae8e844","tid":2442754,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"牙腸戒咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:38:15.